Noel Ferrier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noel_Ferrier 0 Noel Ferrier AM (20 December 1930 – 16 October 1997) was an Australian television personality, comedian, stage and film actor, raconteur and theatrical producer. He had an extensive theatre career which spanned over fifty years.
